gaia.cu9.ari.gaiaorbit.data.stars

Class HYGBinaryLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • gaia.cu9.ari.gaiaorbit.data.stars.AbstractCatalogLoader
      • gaia.cu9.ari.gaiaorbit.data.stars.HYGBinaryLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISceneGraphLoader

    public class HYGBinaryLoader
extends AbstractCatalogLoader
implements ISceneGraphLoader
    Loads the HYG catalog in binary (own) format. The format is defined as follows - 32 bits (int) with the number of stars, starNum repeat the following starNum times (for each star) - 32 bits (int) - The the length of the name, or nameLength - 16 bits * nameLength (chars) - The name of the star - 32 bits (float) - appmag - 32 bits (float) - absmag - 32 bits (float) - colorbv - 32 bits (float) - ra - 32 bits (float) - dec - 32 bits (float) - distance - 64 bits (long) - id
    Author:
    Toni Sagrista
